{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363160/extras/ezgif.com-animated-gif-maker_15.gif?t=1739233944\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>I'm Kazfiel Balthioul Tabbris.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In short, Kaz!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Welcome to the game where being an asshole to your friends <strong>is actually a good thing!</strong> 2-4 players control a single angel. You need each other to survive, but never forget about your own agenda<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363160/extras/Haphazard_Headers__3_.gif?t=1739233944\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Share one body!</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>2-4 players</strong> - Grab a  friend and some controllers, you'll have to work together to achieve objectives! Perfect for parties and game nights!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>1 Angel, 4 Wings</strong>\u00a0- Each player controls one wing, but you all share a single body. Communication is key\u2014good luck with that!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>7 Deadly Sins - </strong>Choose a wing inspired by the seven deadly sins. Each one comes with its own strengths and weaknesses\u2014some complement, others clash. Can you make it work?</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363160/extras/Haphazard_Headers__4_.gif?t=1739233944\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Several Ways To Win. Find Them All!</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Cooperating is a must - </strong>Kaz can't get anywhere with one wing. Collecting halos can get Kaz back to heaven!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Competing is inevitable\u00a0</strong>- Only one wing can pick up halos and evil essences. The more each player picks up, the stronger their influence over Kazfiel gets.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363160/extras/Haphazard_Headers__5_.gif?t=1739233944\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>The controls are simple:</strong> flap your wings, navigate the chaos, and work (or fight) with your teammates. Whether you\u2019re playing couch co-op or online, Haphazard Angel delivers the perfect mix of fun and frustration!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363160/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1739233944","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363160/page.bg.jpg?t=1739233944","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363160/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1739233944","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363160/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1739233944","categories":[{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"PvP","id":49},{"description":"Online PvP","id":36},{"description":"Shared/Split Screen PvP","id":37},{"description":"Co-op","id":9},{"description":"Online Co-op","id":38},{"description":"Shared/Split Screen Co-op","id":39},{"description":"Shared/Split Screen","id":24},{"description":"Cross-Platform Multiplayer","id":27},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28},{"description":"Remote Play Together","id":44}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363160/extras/ezgif.com-animated-gif-maker_15.gif?t=1739233944\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><stron